text: Modern design yet calming and tranquil ambience during the night. It accommodates students well with many facilities such as LTs, studying rooms, Gyms, canteen and swimming pool. Has been taking these for granted as I use them daily.

Great and peaceful place inside National university, especially around the "NUS Green" which is rarely found in Singapore. Good to take a walk or even have a small rest there and see all the energize uni students doing activities or studies around you.
That the "deja vu" of my old uni time, and where the dreams started.
Great place to chill and hang out. Though there appears to be an influx of foreign tourists here recently, so it can get quite crowded on weekdays during peak hours.
Lovely place and glad that my kid managed to study this school
Lovely place even if you're not a student of NUS. We bring the kids here at least once a week to run and play on the lawn. Super windy place, full of affordable places to eat!
